article.description: — Zac Ervin had a career-high 29 points as Elon defeated the NAIA's Bluefield College 89-72 on Sunday.
article.headline: Ervin scores 29 to carry Elon over Bluefield College 89-72
article.linkText: Ervin scores 29 to carry Elon over Bluefield College 89-72
article.story: ELON, N.C. -- — Zac Ervin had a career-high 29 points as Elon defeated the NAIA's Bluefield College 89-72 on Sunday. Darius Burford had 18 points, 12 rebounds and six assists for Elon (2-1). Michael Graham added 11 points and 11 rebounds. Hunter Woods had 10 points. Jermiah Jenkins had 20 points for the Ramblin' Rams. Christian Bullock added 16 points. Wilcliff Senatus had 10 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
